| GNU/Linux  | Red Hat        | Enterprise Linux 8.1 (x86_64) | 3.6.8  |
+------------+----------------+-------------------------------+--------+
| GNU/Linux  | Ubuntu         | 18.04 LTS (amd64)             | 3.6.8  |
+------------+----------------+-------------------------------+--------+
| GNU/Linux  | Ubuntu         | 19.10 (amd64)                 | 3.7.5  |
+------------+----------------+-------------------------------+--------+
| Unix       | Darwin         | macOS 10.14 (x86_64)          | 3.6.9* |
