+------------+----------------+-------------------------------+--------+
| Unix       | Oracle Solaris | 11.4 (x86_64)                 | 3.5.3  |
+------------+----------------+-------------------------------+--------+

Note: (*) above denotes a non-native (third-party) Python interpreter.

